Description: Code to reproduce the Figure 'Traditional biomass and Wood fuel' 
    of the chapter 3 of the IPBES Sustainable Use Assessment. This figure shows 
    two maps a) the population relying on traditional biomass and b) the local 
    wood fuel supply/demand balance.
